WEBVTT

00:08.421 --> 00:11.241
I just want to break free
from this cage,

00:11.980 --> 00:14.001
to live without going against my heart.

00:14.101 --> 00:15.881
Is that too much to ask?

00:17.061 --> 00:18.681
You see your grandfather

00:21.101 --> 00:22.960
as a cage?

00:24.421 --> 00:25.299
Can't you see

00:25.300 --> 00:28.299
how I shield you from hardship
every day?

00:28.300 --> 00:30.960
Do you think tinkering
with those things every day

00:31.221 --> 00:33.841
will make everything go your way?

00:35.620 --> 00:38.841
You're naive to the point
of foolishness.

00:40.020 --> 00:42.801
All under heaven is the emperor's land.

00:43.340 --> 00:47.920
When fame and fortune turn to emptiness,

00:48.541 --> 00:51.441
a true cage will await you.

01:23.820 --> 01:24.620
Sir,

01:24.621 --> 01:26.120
Physician Li has arrived.

01:36.900 --> 01:39.881
Please invite Physician Li
to see the young master.

01:40.380 --> 01:41.200
Yes.

01:46.100 --> 01:47.521
Send the physician away.

01:48.380 --> 01:49.539
I won't see him.

01:49.540 --> 01:50.580
The physician told us

01:50.581 --> 01:51.700
to present this item

01:51.701 --> 01:53.721
if the young master refuses to see him.

03:18.721 --> 03:22.760
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

03:22.761 --> 03:25.981
=Episode 9=

03:26.820 --> 03:29.400
Today, we part ways, Mr. Chen.

03:29.941 --> 03:31.819
If there has been any neglect
or offense,

03:31.820 --> 03:33.560
please forgive us.

03:33.580 --> 03:35.160
You are too kind, Lord Song.

03:35.621 --> 03:38.241
I am merely a commoner in coarse robes.

03:38.420 --> 03:40.460
I have troubled you for so long
at your residence.

03:40.461 --> 03:42.321
I feel deeply ashamed.

03:42.461 --> 03:46.041
Though I don't favor your character,

03:46.341 --> 03:49.041
I must admit you are a rare talent.

03:49.820 --> 03:53.000
Why lower yourself to serve
a girl from a rural manor?

03:58.140 --> 04:01.819
I am a sinner, tainted and disgraced.

04:01.820 --> 04:04.160
Now, in my old age,

04:04.741 --> 04:06.539
the Fourth Young Lady
for not abandoning me,

04:06.540 --> 04:07.960
taking me as her aide,

04:08.380 --> 04:10.180
and allowing me to live out
my days in peace.

04:10.181 --> 04:11.481
For that, I am content.

04:12.301 --> 04:14.601
Your loyalty to the Fourth Young Lady

04:14.781 --> 04:18.000
only piques my curiosity about her.

04:30.140 --> 04:32.281
Thankfully, the chill
hasn't reached the lungs.

04:34.260 --> 04:37.680
From now on, take two doses
in the morning and evening.

04:38.861 --> 04:40.620
Young master, you must
take your medicine.

04:40.621 --> 04:42.541
My lady risked danger to come here.

04:42.541 --> 04:43.479
Do not disappoint her.

04:43.480 --> 04:44.361
Mind your words.

04:50.861 --> 04:52.660
I thought I made myself clear last time,

04:52.661 --> 04:54.440
young master.

04:55.900 --> 04:58.721
All worldly matters pale
in comparison to life itself.

04:59.621 --> 05:01.320
Why trouble yourself, young master?

05:03.140 --> 05:04.660
I didn't mean to use my illness

05:04.661 --> 05:05.961
to coerce you.

05:09.061 --> 05:11.560
It's just that your question last time

05:12.260 --> 05:14.241
struck a chord with me.

05:15.140 --> 05:18.000
I understand how you feel.

05:18.661 --> 05:19.779
But, Mr. Wu,

05:19.780 --> 05:22.161
did your grandfather consult you

05:22.780 --> 05:24.841
when he assigned you
to the Ministry of Rites?

05:25.900 --> 05:28.000
Even you have no control
over your own fate.

05:28.580 --> 05:30.841
Why think about protecting someone else?

05:32.861 --> 05:34.601
I have always respected my grandfather.

05:35.621 --> 05:39.041
He was never wrong about anything.

05:40.580 --> 05:42.200
But when it comes to marriage,

05:43.140 --> 05:45.080
I cannot base it solely
on right or wrong

05:46.181 --> 05:47.760
and ignore my own wishes.

05:51.580 --> 05:54.161
If I weren't born into this
prestigious family,

05:56.900 --> 05:59.080
and instead became a humble carpenter,

06:00.981 --> 06:02.721
would I be freer?

06:03.941 --> 06:05.601
Though men and women are different,

06:06.621 --> 06:08.440
when it comes to marriage,

06:09.460 --> 06:11.361
you and I face similar struggles.

06:13.260 --> 06:15.241
You liken yourself to this wooden bird,

06:15.340 --> 06:16.680
I understand.

06:18.941 --> 06:20.481
But have you ever considered

06:20.603 --> 06:22.721
that in the Grand Secretariat,
people come and go,

06:23.351 --> 06:25.019
yet your grandfather
struggles tirelessly

06:25.020 --> 06:26.601
to maintain order in the court.

06:27.340 --> 06:28.921
Regardless of whether you marry,

06:29.101 --> 06:30.921
he needs your support.

06:31.741 --> 06:33.139
Had you excelled in your career

06:33.140 --> 06:35.041
and restored power to the Wu family,

06:35.140 --> 06:37.201
he would have no reason
to pressure you to marry.

06:38.260 --> 06:40.000
You can earn your freedom,

06:40.421 --> 06:43.200
no matter what family you're born into.

06:50.260 --> 06:51.721
I've been too narrow-minded,

06:51.821 --> 06:53.721
trapped in my own dead-end thinking.

06:55.020 --> 06:56.760
Opposing my grandfather

06:56.981 --> 06:58.481
will only hurt us both.

07:00.621 --> 07:02.481
If I can gain the Emperor's favor

07:03.140 --> 07:04.721
and restore the Wu family's power,

07:05.421 --> 07:09.041
then I will have the right
to choose for myself.

07:10.301 --> 07:12.000
Humans are not lifeless objects.

07:12.020 --> 07:13.560
Even if trapped in a cage,

07:13.741 --> 07:15.200
we must nurture our strength

07:15.580 --> 07:17.721
so that we may fend for ourselves.

07:28.181 --> 07:29.440
Dawn is breaking.

07:31.140 --> 07:32.281
I must take my leave.

07:47.380 --> 07:48.320
Lord Song,

07:48.741 --> 07:51.241
my lady specifically sent me
to fetch Mr. Chen.

07:54.741 --> 07:56.081
She didn't come herself?

07:56.181 --> 07:57.841
Did something urgent come up?

07:57.941 --> 07:59.379
I am only following orders,

07:59.380 --> 08:00.620
I know nothing else.

08:00.621 --> 08:01.880
Please understand.

08:03.301 --> 08:05.760
Our young lord has always
been accommodating,

08:05.981 --> 08:08.000
but sending a maid
instead of coming herself

08:08.140 --> 08:10.721
seems a little disrespectful.

08:13.020 --> 08:13.921
Lu Ming,

08:14.741 --> 08:15.801
send the gift back

08:15.861 --> 08:17.361
to Fourth Young Lady as well.

08:17.661 --> 08:18.219
Yes.

08:18.220 --> 08:19.259
Farewell.

08:19.260 --> 08:20.200
Wait.

08:27.541 --> 08:28.560
Physician Li.

08:30.311 --> 08:32.579
The Fourth Young Lady disguised herself
as Physician Li.

08:32.580 --> 08:33.819
I've captured Su Lan.

08:33.820 --> 08:35.400
She's in the carriage right now.

08:43.521 --> 08:46.781
(Report)

08:52.980 --> 08:54.699
Physician Li, thank you
for your hard work.

08:54.700 --> 08:56.099
You may leave for now.

08:56.100 --> 08:58.640
Thank you, my lord.

09:03.340 --> 09:04.120
Lu Ming.

09:04.541 --> 09:05.241
Yes.

09:05.860 --> 09:08.760
Go invite the Fourth Young Lady here.

09:08.781 --> 09:09.441
Yes.

09:15.661 --> 09:16.681
Fourth Young Lady.

09:18.661 --> 09:22.441
Can we meet for a fifth time?

09:23.661 --> 09:25.481
Even if you don't change your mind,

09:25.901 --> 09:26.841
I'd be happy

09:27.580 --> 09:29.081
just to see you again.

09:30.781 --> 09:33.081
If you could live happily and freely,

09:33.460 --> 09:35.201
wouldn't that be better than seeing me?

09:36.620 --> 09:37.361
Take care.

09:57.980 --> 09:58.880
Old Master Wu.

09:59.740 --> 10:00.961
After you, Physician.

10:02.901 --> 10:03.760
Wait.

10:07.661 --> 10:08.520
Grandfather.

10:10.580 --> 10:13.681
She's the imperial physician
Yantang invited.

10:14.460 --> 10:15.961
Imperial physician?

10:18.021 --> 10:22.361
Would you mind turning around
and let me take a look?

10:40.580 --> 10:41.601
Physician Li.

10:43.781 --> 10:44.721
Old Master Wu.

10:45.021 --> 10:46.339
Lord Song and Physician Li

10:46.340 --> 10:48.060
have arranged to meet at Guanghe Tower.

10:48.061 --> 10:50.040
He sent me to invite Physician Li.

10:54.220 --> 10:55.481
Since that's the case,

10:56.381 --> 10:59.400
I won't hold you up any longer.

11:07.500 --> 11:09.961
You're finally willing to see
a physician.

11:11.181 --> 11:12.601
I'm guessing

11:13.700 --> 11:15.561
her surname is Dou?

11:17.220 --> 11:19.000
Now that you've seen her,

11:19.820 --> 11:21.561
be sure to rest well.

11:24.421 --> 11:25.241
Grandfather.

11:27.500 --> 11:30.201
I was wrong.

11:32.740 --> 11:34.000
Since my early education,

11:35.261 --> 11:37.561
everything in my life
has been decided by you.

11:38.941 --> 11:42.040
What books to read, whom to befriend,

11:43.181 --> 11:44.800
which teachers to study under,

11:46.620 --> 11:48.160
and where to serve as an official.

11:48.941 --> 11:51.640
Even what I eat for breakfast
is arranged by you.

11:53.860 --> 11:56.721
Sometimes, I truly envy Dou Zhao,

11:59.381 --> 12:00.841
and also Yantang,

12:02.100 --> 12:03.961
for their freedom
and lack of constraints.

12:18.021 --> 12:18.841
Grandfather,

12:19.580 --> 12:22.321
I know the court is treacherous

12:22.381 --> 12:23.681
and unpredictable.

12:24.021 --> 12:27.481
Our entire family relies solely
on your strength.

12:30.700 --> 12:32.321
I will strive diligently

12:32.700 --> 12:35.561
to weather these challenges with you.

12:53.220 --> 12:54.800
Under Dou Shishu's order,

12:55.460 --> 12:57.920
the Ding Army has been fully disarmed.

12:58.100 --> 13:00.219
The army is accused
of harboring rebellious intent

13:00.220 --> 13:02.321
and has been sent back
to their hometowns.

13:03.661 --> 13:05.841
The Fourth Young Lady
kept you occupied here,

13:06.980 --> 13:08.880
and even tied up Physician Li.

13:22.580 --> 13:24.441
The court has acted against
the Ding Army.

13:25.421 --> 13:26.681
It's Fifth Uncle.

13:26.841 --> 13:28.780
Previously, I took great risks
to save Song Mo,

13:28.781 --> 13:31.601
and through our interactions,
his hostility had all but disappeared.

13:32.700 --> 13:34.280
But in the end, it was all in vain.

13:39.580 --> 13:40.321
My lord,

13:40.428 --> 13:42.561
the Fourth Young Lady's carriage
will arrive shortly.

13:44.700 --> 13:45.681
Good.

13:46.941 --> 13:49.561
Convey my regards to her.

13:50.220 --> 13:50.961
Yes.

13:59.340 --> 14:00.961
Fourth Young Lady, there's an issue.

14:12.541 --> 14:15.361
Openly do one thing while secretly
planning something else.

14:15.460 --> 14:17.201
Very clever, Fourth Young Lady.

14:17.580 --> 14:18.880
On behalf of Lord Song,

14:19.340 --> 14:20.321
may I request

14:21.100 --> 14:22.441
an explanation?

14:39.541 --> 14:41.000
There's nothing to explain.

14:55.100 --> 14:56.520
My lord says,

14:56.620 --> 14:57.859
since the pact is broken,

14:57.860 --> 15:00.400
we will not return Chen Qushui.

15:00.620 --> 15:01.561
Next time we meet,

15:02.620 --> 15:04.120
you'll be considered an enemy.

15:15.700 --> 15:17.520
My lady, why didn't you
explain yourself?

15:17.580 --> 15:19.099
It was all Master Dou Shishu's doing,

15:19.100 --> 15:20.561
and has nothing to do with you.

15:23.500 --> 15:24.721
If he trusts me,

15:25.353 --> 15:26.681
there's no need to explain.

15:28.061 --> 15:29.280
If he doesn't trust me,

15:30.041 --> 15:31.321
an explanation is useless.

15:32.340 --> 15:33.520
Better to remain silent.

15:34.541 --> 15:36.081
Miss, don't blame yourself.

15:36.141 --> 15:38.361
The imperial will is not something
we can defy anyway.

15:42.261 --> 15:42.977
My lord,

15:42.978 --> 15:44.478
are you letting it go just like that?

15:45.261 --> 15:46.481
The truth of the matter

15:46.820 --> 15:48.081
is still uncertain.

15:48.860 --> 15:51.280
If her intention was to first
show kindness and then scheme,

15:52.100 --> 15:54.120
why would she console Dezhen?

15:56.340 --> 15:57.441
Let's wait and see.

15:59.061 --> 16:00.540
My lord, despite all your precautions,

16:00.541 --> 16:02.040
your emotions are still vulnerable.

16:02.781 --> 16:04.561
The Fourth Young Lady is unpredictable,

16:04.781 --> 16:06.120
and you are soft-hearted.

16:06.181 --> 16:08.020
Why not just marry her
and keep her at home?

16:08.021 --> 16:09.880
That way, you'd be safe.

16:09.881 --> 16:11.099
Are you itching for a beating?

16:11.100 --> 16:12.140
Want a taste of the rod?

16:12.141 --> 16:13.000
I...

16:15.781 --> 16:17.040
There you are.

16:19.500 --> 16:22.361
The Shadow Guards have found
the travel records.

16:31.941 --> 16:33.160
As expected,

16:33.500 --> 16:35.160
one person slipped through.

16:39.100 --> 16:41.201
Owing 300 taels
and still daring to cheat?

16:42.301 --> 16:43.000
Addicted.

16:43.141 --> 16:44.361
And bold as well.

16:46.340 --> 16:47.481
I told you,

16:47.860 --> 16:50.140
someone will settle my debt.

16:50.141 --> 16:51.841
Do you think I'm a fool?

16:53.620 --> 16:56.000
If you kill him, you'll get nothing.

16:58.700 --> 17:00.441
Our young master has questions.

17:01.061 --> 17:02.920
Please clear the place for us.

17:04.980 --> 17:06.881
There's the person
who will settle my debt.

17:10.641 --> 17:12.721
You used to be a junior officer
in the Shadow Guard.

17:12.780 --> 17:14.280
Given your former rank,

17:14.381 --> 17:16.320
your annual stipend
was no more than ten taels.

17:16.740 --> 17:19.121
In just a few days, you've incurred
a debt of 300 taels.

17:19.621 --> 17:21.681
No wonder you were dismissed.

17:21.980 --> 17:24.241
Compared to the information you seek,

17:24.861 --> 17:27.241
300-tael debt is insignificant.

17:31.460 --> 17:33.000
Cheat the house,

17:33.101 --> 17:34.641
and you lose your finger.

17:34.700 --> 17:36.241
Cheat me,

17:36.941 --> 17:38.161
and you lose your life.

17:38.621 --> 17:39.600
Of course.

17:43.581 --> 17:45.320
Surely, you've looked
into my background.

17:45.321 --> 17:47.431
According to the records
of the Pacification Bureau,

17:47.441 --> 17:50.320
there were eight Shadow Guards assigned
to escort southward.

17:50.461 --> 17:52.580
I traced the waterways
outlined in the travel records

17:52.581 --> 17:55.040
in order to identify
these eight individuals.

17:55.661 --> 17:57.280
But the travel record shows

17:58.060 --> 17:59.560
that there was a ninth person.

18:02.381 --> 18:03.481
And you

18:04.381 --> 18:06.641
are that ninth person.

18:08.281 --> 18:09.660
(Zhaowen Bookstore)

18:09.661 --> 18:10.641
Ansu,

18:11.281 --> 18:12.681
why did you come here so suddenly?

18:14.460 --> 18:16.280
(Urgent letter to Dou Zhao)
Mr. Ji sent a letter from Futing.

18:16.421 --> 18:20.059
Officials from the Maritime Trade Bureau
detained our ship and imprisoned my family.

18:20.060 --> 18:21.681
Fifth Master sent word to the manor,

18:22.141 --> 18:24.360
ordering you to sever ties
with my family

18:24.500 --> 18:26.401
and end all business dealings.

18:30.220 --> 18:31.059
But on that ship,

18:31.060 --> 18:32.979
there were only eight
Shadow Guard corpses.

18:32.980 --> 18:34.820
I remember every single face

18:34.821 --> 18:36.600
among them.

18:43.421 --> 18:45.080
Except for you, Chen Jia.

18:45.740 --> 18:47.320
You weren't on that ship.

18:49.300 --> 18:51.481
Your memory is truly eidetic,

18:52.341 --> 18:53.900
just as everyone says.

18:53.901 --> 18:56.040
Enough chatter. Tell us the truth!

18:56.841 --> 18:59.620
Chen Zuxun, the commander responsible
for escorting the Duke of Ding,

18:59.621 --> 19:00.840
was my adoptive father.

19:01.181 --> 19:03.241
My name was not listed
in the official roster.

19:03.821 --> 19:06.401
He wanted me to redeem myself
through merit and took me along.

19:10.761 --> 19:12.921
That night, as we traveled
through the Cangzhou Canal,

19:13.421 --> 19:14.840
we docked to rest briefly.

19:15.421 --> 19:17.600
A group of people boarded the ship.

19:24.941 --> 19:26.401
I was at the stern getting fresh air

19:26.821 --> 19:28.921
when I suddenly heard a clash
in the cabin.

19:30.101 --> 19:31.961
They wielded the swords
of Dongyu bandits,

19:31.980 --> 19:34.441
but their technique was different
from Dongyu bandits.

19:34.740 --> 19:36.040
Their skills were extraordinary,

19:36.421 --> 19:38.121
even the Shadow Guards
couldn't match them.

19:41.980 --> 19:43.800
They even killed my adoptive father.

19:47.260 --> 19:48.921
I was no match for them.

19:49.861 --> 19:53.161
I escaped by jumping into the water
during the chaos.

19:56.780 --> 19:58.360
Who were those people?

19:59.861 --> 20:01.481
If you want to know more,

20:03.621 --> 20:05.401
a thousand taels may not be enough.

20:10.460 --> 20:12.080
You clearly don't know,

20:13.020 --> 20:15.201
yet you dare bargain with me.

20:16.101 --> 20:17.641
Ring finger or little finger?

20:19.460 --> 20:20.881
I'm a gambler by nature.

20:22.260 --> 20:24.360
I've endured enough cold stares
and debts.

20:25.161 --> 20:27.620
The only one who ever treated me
as human, my adoptive father,

20:27.621 --> 20:28.760
died a wrongful death.

20:29.780 --> 20:31.600
Whether it's my fingers or my life,

20:32.621 --> 20:34.320
take whatever you want.

20:43.220 --> 20:45.800
A dog salivates at the sound
of a bowl being struck.

20:46.341 --> 20:48.760
A gambler relapses at the sound
of dice shaking.

20:49.341 --> 20:51.620
With your skills, you could've built
a decent future.

20:51.621 --> 20:54.131
That's probably why your adoptive father
never gave up on you.

20:54.220 --> 20:56.760
It's a pity he made such a poor choice.

20:57.260 --> 20:59.121
You have no right to talk
about him like that.

21:01.821 --> 21:03.641
A child's debt to his parents
is immeasurable.

21:03.941 --> 21:05.059
The people who killed him

21:05.060 --> 21:07.280
are the same people who killed my uncle.

21:07.500 --> 21:09.641
Instead of seeking vengeance
or repaying his kindness,

21:09.661 --> 21:11.539
you squander your days gambling

21:11.540 --> 21:12.921
and live without purpose?

21:18.341 --> 21:20.080
I saw through the lies a long time ago.

21:22.821 --> 21:24.241
Whether a junior officer

21:25.060 --> 21:26.441
or a commander,

21:27.780 --> 21:30.600
the Shadow Guards are merely tools
at others' disposal,

21:31.661 --> 21:34.241
ants to be crushed at will.

21:36.060 --> 21:36.921
As for revenge,

21:38.540 --> 21:40.721
I will never achieve it
even if I risk my life.

21:42.300 --> 21:44.040
I don't know who those people were,

21:44.700 --> 21:46.651
but the leader wore
crimson official robes,

21:46.661 --> 21:48.527
so he must be at least
a fifth-rank official.

21:48.528 --> 21:51.340
Even my adoptive father allowed him
to pass and addressed him as "sir."

21:52.381 --> 21:54.140
He must be a high-ranking
court official.

21:54.141 --> 21:56.499
Why did the Shadow Guards
torture my uncle?

21:56.500 --> 21:57.581
Secret orders.

21:57.591 --> 21:59.539
The instructions were to force
the Duke of Ding

21:59.540 --> 22:01.100
to confess to raising a private army.

22:01.101 --> 22:02.401
Whose secret orders?

22:05.421 --> 22:06.961
My adoptive father never disclosed it.

22:13.700 --> 22:14.560
My lord.

22:16.460 --> 22:18.320
I didn't have the courage before.

22:19.941 --> 22:21.241
But after meeting you today,

22:21.421 --> 22:22.961
and hearing your words,

22:24.581 --> 22:25.459
I no longer wish

22:25.460 --> 22:27.161
to live disgracefully.

22:28.260 --> 22:30.961
I want revenge.

22:32.381 --> 22:34.600
I want to live with dignity and purpose.

22:35.260 --> 22:36.860
Please grant me this chance.

22:36.861 --> 22:38.499
I am willing to stake my life.

22:38.500 --> 22:41.201
How can I trust the words
of a cheating gambler?

22:50.060 --> 22:51.600
Ask the Earl of Yunyang to help

22:51.601 --> 22:53.681
reinstate him into the
Northern Pacification Bureau.

22:54.540 --> 22:55.059
Yes.

22:55.060 --> 22:56.840
From now on, you are one of my men.

22:58.020 --> 22:59.241
Keep your finger.

22:59.621 --> 23:03.360
You're going to need it to fight for me.

23:11.141 --> 23:12.560
Zhao, don't worry.

23:12.581 --> 23:14.420
The Maritime Trade Bureau
has always been

23:14.421 --> 23:16.100
all bark but no bite.

23:16.101 --> 23:17.760
They just want a little bribe.

23:17.821 --> 23:19.560
I'll go to Futing to handle it.

23:19.621 --> 23:21.820
After all, this concerns your principal

23:21.821 --> 23:22.760
and profits.

23:23.941 --> 23:25.080
I'll go with you.

23:25.500 --> 23:26.921
What about Mr. Chen?

23:27.941 --> 23:29.161
Knowing Song Mo,

23:29.821 --> 23:31.520
he won't simply harm Mr. Chen.

23:31.780 --> 23:32.699
No.

23:32.700 --> 23:34.481
Fifth Master has already sent a message.

23:34.491 --> 23:36.691
If the Maritime Trade Bureau
were only seeking bribes,

23:37.300 --> 23:39.000
Fifth Uncle wouldn't have known about it.

23:39.421 --> 23:40.721
Since he knows,

23:41.141 --> 23:43.201
that means it must involve
court politics.

23:43.821 --> 23:45.211
I have to go.

23:45.221 --> 23:47.060
Futing hasn't yet recovered
from the disaster.

23:47.061 --> 23:48.203
The troops are frustrated,

23:48.203 --> 23:50.251
even the Ministry of Imperial
Ceremony is involved.

23:50.281 --> 23:52.040
It's clearly in a perilous situation.

23:52.151 --> 23:54.201
That's all the more reason
you shouldn't go, Zhao.

23:54.381 --> 23:55.560
No matter what happens,

23:55.661 --> 23:57.560
I will ensure your principal
is returned.

23:59.060 --> 24:00.641
What nonsense are you talking about?

24:01.260 --> 24:02.921
I don't care about money.

24:03.381 --> 24:05.520
I care about your family
and our business.

24:05.621 --> 24:06.340
We can't let them

24:06.341 --> 24:08.161
manipulate us like this.

24:08.581 --> 24:09.560
I'll go.

24:10.220 --> 24:11.961
At least I can try to negotiate
a way out.

24:13.001 --> 24:15.501
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

24:19.861 --> 24:20.760
Yantang.

24:26.341 --> 24:27.241
Mother.

24:29.060 --> 24:30.201
Why are you out here?

24:30.381 --> 24:31.600
General Yan said

24:31.801 --> 24:34.201
you were going to Futing to retrieve
old family belongings.

24:35.220 --> 24:36.961
It may fool your father,

24:37.181 --> 24:38.360
but not me.

24:39.581 --> 24:41.100
Is it about your uncle?

24:41.101 --> 24:42.560
Did you find any clues?

24:46.221 --> 24:48.241
This involves someone
with high rank and authority.

24:48.421 --> 24:49.760
I must leave immediately.

24:50.300 --> 24:51.320
If I'm late,

24:52.181 --> 24:54.080
I fear all evidence and clues
will be lost.

24:54.901 --> 24:56.280
You're just like me,

24:57.381 --> 25:00.401
once you've made up your mind,
no one can stop you.

25:01.941 --> 25:04.721
The Emperor has put Wang Yuan
in charge of this matter.

25:05.260 --> 25:07.380
When you go,
no matter what you uncover,

25:07.381 --> 25:09.600
do not oppose Eunuch Wang directly.

25:10.901 --> 25:11.961
General Yan,

25:12.341 --> 25:13.481
I leave this to you.

25:13.901 --> 25:15.600
Please don't worry, Madam.

25:15.621 --> 25:16.560
Mother,

25:17.540 --> 25:18.360
rest assured.

25:19.300 --> 25:20.921
Stay safe.

25:21.740 --> 25:23.201
Don't push yourself too hard.

25:26.260 --> 25:28.481
I've already lost my brother.

25:29.941 --> 25:31.800
I can't lose you too.

25:38.101 --> 25:40.560
Here, take this cloak.

25:41.641 --> 25:44.301
♪The army halts at your command♪

25:44.341 --> 25:47.520
Good thing I've mended this cloak.

25:51.321 --> 25:53.800
♪The golden fiery steed
rides across the vast horizon♪

25:53.801 --> 26:02.340
♪In this life, oh without you
What is there to envy?♪

26:02.341 --> 26:02.940
Go now.

26:02.941 --> 26:06.120
♪Let me lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

26:06.121 --> 26:10.421
♪To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin♪

26:12.661 --> 26:13.560
Mother,

26:14.181 --> 26:15.161
I'll be back.

26:17.441 --> 26:23.200
♪Only for you, I shall paint
With bold strokes and vibrant colors♪

26:23.201 --> 26:32.381
♪And for all else
Let it remain pale and void♪

26:42.421 --> 26:43.840
What's wrong with Zhao?

26:44.581 --> 26:46.560
She's been like this
since meeting Lord Song.

26:46.740 --> 26:49.059
She's probably worried

26:49.060 --> 26:50.600
because Mr. Chen hasn't returned.

26:52.581 --> 26:53.739
Zhao,

26:53.740 --> 26:54.860
why don't you eat something?

26:54.861 --> 26:56.161
You haven't eaten all day.

26:57.460 --> 26:59.760
I'm not hungry. You all eat first.

27:04.901 --> 27:07.161
I wonder how the manor is doing.

27:07.381 --> 27:08.760
Will there be any trouble?

27:18.421 --> 27:20.699
The Fourth Young Lady's pulse
is strong and steady.

27:20.700 --> 27:22.539
It seems there's nothing wrong.

27:22.540 --> 27:24.019
How could there be nothing wrong?

27:24.020 --> 27:26.121
Dou Zhao is covered in blisters
and itching terribly.

27:26.381 --> 27:28.280
Are you a quack?

27:29.901 --> 27:32.121
Why don't you check again?

27:34.901 --> 27:35.681
Wait.

27:36.780 --> 27:38.259
Her pulse is fluctuating.

27:38.260 --> 27:39.800
Peculiar...

27:39.821 --> 27:40.961
Very peculiar indeed!

27:41.141 --> 27:42.660
By the way, Fourth Young Lady,

27:42.661 --> 27:44.100
could I take a look

27:44.101 --> 27:45.459
at your blisters?

27:45.460 --> 27:47.059
Take a look?

27:47.060 --> 27:48.580
She's an unmarried young lady.

27:48.581 --> 27:50.100
How audacious of you.

27:50.101 --> 27:50.420
Get out.

27:50.421 --> 27:50.860
No, I...

27:50.861 --> 27:51.860
Go prescribe medicine.

27:51.861 --> 27:53.080
Easy...

27:53.341 --> 27:54.280
Grandmother.

27:54.421 --> 27:55.580
How is Dou Zhao doing?

27:55.581 --> 27:56.681
Let me see her.

27:56.861 --> 27:57.900
Please don't.

27:57.901 --> 27:59.259
Dou Zhao has chickenpox.

27:59.260 --> 28:00.580
If you catch it,

28:00.581 --> 28:01.539
we'll all be worried.

28:01.540 --> 28:03.620
The doctor has already gone
to prescribe medicine.

28:03.621 --> 28:05.420
She should recover in ten days or so.

28:05.421 --> 28:06.979
Medicine alone won't help.

28:06.980 --> 28:09.560
This disease is terribly painful
to endure.

28:09.700 --> 28:11.161
Let me take a look at her.

28:11.300 --> 28:12.219
Grandmother...

28:12.220 --> 28:12.820
Wait,

28:12.821 --> 28:14.161
don't come in.

28:14.381 --> 28:16.080
You haven't fully recovered yourself.

28:16.181 --> 28:18.000
If you catch chickenpox from me,

28:18.060 --> 28:19.881
I'll feel even more guilty.

28:20.540 --> 28:21.420
See?

28:21.421 --> 28:22.299
That's why I said,

28:22.300 --> 28:23.580
since I've had chickenpox before,

28:23.581 --> 28:25.459
let me take care of her.

28:25.460 --> 28:28.100
You should go back and rest.

28:28.101 --> 28:28.900
Don't worry,

28:28.901 --> 28:31.660
I promise to return Dou Zhao to you,
healthy and plump in a few days.

28:31.661 --> 28:32.620
- Are you sure?
- Go.

28:32.621 --> 28:33.520
You too, go.

28:34.101 --> 28:35.560
Don't worry. I've got this.

28:38.060 --> 28:40.161
Oh, heavens, gods of fortune,
and Guan Yu,

28:40.181 --> 28:42.441
please bless Dou Zhao and Ansu
with a safe return.

28:44.941 --> 28:47.219
Fifth Master has been promoted
to Right Censor-in-Chief,

28:47.220 --> 28:49.201
and Mr. Wang has joined the Secretariat.

28:49.381 --> 28:51.481
We'll be interacting with them often
from now on.

28:51.581 --> 28:52.739
Our lives

28:52.740 --> 28:54.820
will only improve
with Madam Wang's help.

28:54.821 --> 28:57.040
We just need to sit back and watch

28:57.060 --> 28:58.881
the money we entrusted to her grow.

29:00.901 --> 29:01.600
I win!

29:04.980 --> 29:06.080
Seventh Madam.

29:09.020 --> 29:10.280
Excuse me for a moment.

29:12.700 --> 29:14.840
Whose turn is it to draw a tile?

29:16.300 --> 29:17.241
Seventh Madam.

29:17.780 --> 29:18.900
Someone saw Fourth Young Lady

29:18.901 --> 29:21.161
and Miss Miao leaving the city gate

29:21.300 --> 29:22.881
and heading south.

29:23.821 --> 29:25.401
Understood. You may leave.

29:25.500 --> 29:26.280
Yes.

29:31.740 --> 29:33.600
They're probably heading to Futing.

29:34.381 --> 29:35.699
The Miao family's merchant ships

29:35.700 --> 29:38.280
were detained in Futing
by the Maritime Trade Bureau.

29:39.091 --> 29:41.800
Of course they're anxious,
their source of income has been cut off.

29:41.941 --> 29:44.091
A young lady leaving the household
without permission,

29:44.300 --> 29:46.080
isn't that a disgrace to the family?

29:46.460 --> 29:47.900
She's practically handing us

29:47.901 --> 29:49.600
leverage against her.

29:49.780 --> 29:51.961
Let's bring her back
and hold her accountable.

29:53.341 --> 29:54.241
No need to rush.

29:54.381 --> 29:56.560
If we capture her now,

29:56.861 --> 29:58.201
her punishment would be

29:58.540 --> 30:01.000
a few days of kneeling at most.

30:01.220 --> 30:03.600
Then Dou Shiying will pity her again.

30:04.141 --> 30:06.161
That girl likes to stir up trouble,
doesn't she?

30:07.381 --> 30:10.641
Futing is now like a tiger's den.

30:10.661 --> 30:12.921
Let's see how capable she really is.

30:13.081 --> 30:16.781
(Futing)

30:29.341 --> 30:32.280
Spare us some food, please...

30:32.540 --> 30:35.241
We'll trade tea for rice.

30:35.260 --> 30:37.080
Eight measures of tea
for one measure of rice.

30:37.581 --> 30:38.639
No shoving. Here, take it.

30:38.640 --> 30:39.439
Step back, everyone.

30:39.440 --> 30:40.200
No shoving, please.

30:40.201 --> 30:41.060
There's enough.

30:41.061 --> 30:41.779
Here.

30:41.780 --> 30:42.979
No shoving.

30:42.980 --> 30:44.299
There's enough for everyone.

30:44.300 --> 30:45.100
Here.

30:45.101 --> 30:46.280
No shoving.

30:46.581 --> 30:47.481
No shoving.

30:55.581 --> 30:57.420
How did Futing become like this?

30:57.421 --> 30:59.320
The people can't even get a proper meal.

31:00.091 --> 31:03.080
In recent years, the maritime trade
boomed, and tea trading was profitable.

31:03.540 --> 31:05.441
Everyone switched
from growing rice to tea.

31:05.661 --> 31:08.161
After the Duke of Ding's death,
the maritime trade ceased.

31:08.740 --> 31:11.441
Now, they can't sell the tea at all.

31:11.661 --> 31:12.760
Exactly.

31:14.421 --> 31:15.961
And the government does nothing?

31:16.141 --> 31:17.141
Who would dare intervene?

31:17.151 --> 31:19.939
Anyone who does is accused of colluding
with the Miao family merchants.

31:19.940 --> 31:21.459
Several major tea firms invested

31:21.460 --> 31:22.681
in the Miao family's ships.

31:22.700 --> 31:23.900
Now the ships are detained,

31:23.901 --> 31:24.900
the money is gone,

31:24.901 --> 31:26.721
and the goods are still
being held on board.

31:28.741 --> 31:31.340
It's all my father's fault
for being greedy and ignoring advice.

31:31.340 --> 31:33.471
He even got the townsfolk
to invest in shipbuilding,

31:33.481 --> 31:34.841
and now so many people are harmed.

31:35.821 --> 31:37.840
Mr. Miao didn't intend
to deceive anyone.

31:37.861 --> 31:39.121
It's not fair to call it harm.

31:39.181 --> 31:40.721
Halting trade and detaining ships

31:40.740 --> 31:42.800
is what truly cuts off
people's livelihoods.

31:44.341 --> 31:45.641
Once we enter the city,

31:45.661 --> 31:47.201
we should meet with Ji Yong first.

31:47.361 --> 31:49.259
He knows the situation
in Futing's bureaucracy

31:49.260 --> 31:50.940
and the Maritime Trade Bureau's motives

31:50.941 --> 31:52.520
better than we do.

31:53.621 --> 31:54.360
Su Lan,

31:54.460 --> 31:55.620
go buy some dry rations.

31:55.621 --> 31:56.800
We still have a journey ahead.

31:57.020 --> 31:57.641
Got it.

32:03.980 --> 32:04.881
Stop!

32:04.980 --> 32:06.080
Stop right there!

32:09.780 --> 32:11.441
No. Keep moving.

32:14.220 --> 32:14.921
Let's go.

32:20.861 --> 32:22.280
Are you Miss Miao?

32:22.700 --> 32:25.520
Supervisor Ding Wei of the
Maritime Trade Bureau summons you.

32:26.381 --> 32:27.360
And you,

32:27.901 --> 32:29.161
you must be Dou Zhao.

32:29.661 --> 32:30.401
Take them away.

32:52.141 --> 32:53.600
Ji Yong.

33:01.761 --> 33:03.821
(Futing County Office)

33:10.941 --> 33:11.921
Untie them.

33:15.861 --> 33:19.080
The Miao family colluded with pirates,

33:19.101 --> 33:20.681
the evidence is irrefutable.

33:26.341 --> 33:29.241
If you sign, you're admitting guilt.

33:30.020 --> 33:33.961
If you don't sign, the punishment
will be even worse.

33:35.220 --> 33:36.201
Impossible.

33:36.341 --> 33:38.481
My father would never commit treason.

33:39.260 --> 33:41.161
The Miao family runs maritime trade.

33:41.171 --> 33:43.161
The pirates plunder our seas
and kill our people.

33:43.220 --> 33:44.280
We despise them.

33:44.540 --> 33:46.080
Why would we collude with them?

33:48.700 --> 33:50.459
During the previous maritime ban,

33:50.460 --> 33:53.080
how many unruly merchants
colluded with pirates?

33:53.381 --> 33:55.940
Your father must have taken bribes
from some pirates

33:55.941 --> 33:58.681
to engage in such a heinous act.

33:59.680 --> 34:00.459
Are you suggesting

34:00.460 --> 34:02.931
the Miao family colluded with pirates
to kill the Duke of Ding?

34:03.941 --> 34:05.940
Murdering a pillar of our nation
is a grave crime,

34:05.941 --> 34:07.320
how can you simply accuse us?

34:08.181 --> 34:11.280
Besides, Eunuch Wang Yuan is in Futing.

34:11.841 --> 34:14.680
How will you explain yourself if this
leads to a miscarriage of justice?

34:15.980 --> 34:17.001
Insolence!

34:17.480 --> 34:19.920
You know this is a serious crime,
yet you're still so defiant.

34:20.020 --> 34:21.880
Bring in the evidence.

34:24.060 --> 34:25.800
Take a good look.

34:25.980 --> 34:27.499
These pirate swords were found aboard

34:27.500 --> 34:28.920
your family's merchant ship.

34:29.701 --> 34:32.360
They're identical to the one
that killed the Duke of Ding.

34:32.980 --> 34:36.280
This is irrefutable proof
of your murderous crime.

34:36.660 --> 34:37.760
Impossible.

34:38.421 --> 34:40.360
I personally kept
the merchant ship's logs.

34:40.460 --> 34:43.179
For this journey, we carried only tea,
fruits, silks, and porcelain.

34:43.180 --> 34:44.459
There were absolutely no weapons.

34:44.460 --> 34:45.539
The escort, Xue Ping,

34:45.540 --> 34:46.740
the goods inspector, Li Gui,

34:46.741 --> 34:48.979
and the Maritime Trade Bureau clerk,
Liu Limu,

34:48.980 --> 34:50.041
can all testify.

34:50.580 --> 34:51.880
Lord Ding, may I ask you,

34:52.500 --> 34:54.019
where are the witnesses?

34:54.020 --> 34:55.179
Yes, where are they?

34:55.180 --> 34:56.260
Where's the testimony?

34:56.261 --> 34:57.601
Where are the witnesses?

34:57.701 --> 34:59.059
Bring them out!

34:59.060 --> 35:00.340
We can't wrong the innocent!

35:00.341 --> 35:01.440
Silence!

35:01.620 --> 35:02.860
It's not your place to tell me

35:02.861 --> 35:04.320
how to conduct my investigation.

35:05.060 --> 35:06.480
You want witnesses?

35:07.060 --> 35:08.760
Aren't you witnesses yourselves?

35:08.901 --> 35:11.241
Guards, take them to the county jail.

35:14.071 --> 35:15.981
Interrogate me if you must,
but don't touch her.

35:15.991 --> 35:18.011
She is the granddaughter
of the Cui family of Ji'an

35:18.021 --> 35:19.860
and the eldest daughter
of the Dou family.

35:19.861 --> 35:21.161
How dare you lay hands on her?

35:21.161 --> 35:22.601
Your family's affairs are my affairs.

35:23.660 --> 35:26.041
I was sent by my family to resolve
this misunderstanding.

35:26.500 --> 35:28.281
The rest of my family
will arrive shortly.

35:28.301 --> 35:30.161
Do you still intend
to fabricate charges?

35:31.500 --> 35:33.201
The relatives of high officials?

35:33.500 --> 35:36.681
Perhaps I'll uncover evidence
of factionalism and corruption too.

35:36.701 --> 35:38.260
That would earn me even more merit.

35:38.261 --> 35:39.280
Take them away!

35:43.881 --> 35:46.501
(Prison)

35:55.980 --> 35:56.840
Stop.

36:01.741 --> 36:04.840
Why isn't the questioning conducted
in the public court,

36:05.460 --> 36:07.440
before the eyes of the citizens?

36:07.821 --> 36:10.480
Are you aware this is an abuse of power?

36:10.941 --> 36:13.480
Using torture to extract a confession
is a serious crime.

36:13.861 --> 36:16.641
Fourth Young Lady Dou,
you're a clever person.

36:16.861 --> 36:20.480
All I need is a confession in writing.

36:20.540 --> 36:23.480
If you admit to the
Miao family's crimes,

36:23.861 --> 36:25.521
you'll be released immediately.

36:26.020 --> 36:28.001
The Miao family has done nothing wrong.

36:28.580 --> 36:30.041
What is there to confess?

36:32.180 --> 36:34.280
Then you leave me no choice

36:34.341 --> 36:36.561
but to say you had your chance.

36:58.301 --> 36:59.800
I interrogated

37:00.301 --> 37:01.480
Miao Ansu.

37:01.701 --> 37:04.320
I pulled out all ten of her fingernails.

37:04.701 --> 37:05.800
Take a good look.

37:06.701 --> 37:08.001
She confessed everything.

37:09.580 --> 37:11.641
Sisterly bonds?

37:11.861 --> 37:14.161
If you don't confess,

37:14.261 --> 37:15.059
you'll be the one

37:15.060 --> 37:17.161
who bears all the blame.

37:19.980 --> 37:21.280
Why are you laughing?

37:21.861 --> 37:23.561
I'm laughing at your stupidity.

37:24.341 --> 37:27.360
Before accusing someone, shouldn't you
do your research first?

37:27.381 --> 37:31.400
Even if someone were to betray me,

37:32.301 --> 37:36.121
Miao Ansu would be the last person
to do so.

37:37.580 --> 37:39.320
Lord Ding, all you're missing
is a witness.

37:39.381 --> 37:42.081
Without it, you can't close the case.

37:43.140 --> 37:44.940
So you're trying to muddle through

37:44.941 --> 37:46.681
by finding a scapegoat.

37:48.980 --> 37:50.121
Very well.

37:50.861 --> 37:53.260
It seems you won't confess

37:53.261 --> 37:55.059
without torture.

37:55.060 --> 37:56.800
Let's see if you dare.

38:04.861 --> 38:05.920
He doesn't dare to.

38:06.741 --> 38:07.601
But I do.

38:09.180 --> 38:10.161
Song Mo!

38:10.861 --> 38:12.121
Lord Song.

38:12.381 --> 38:13.440
Fourth Young Lady.

38:14.301 --> 38:15.561
We meet again.

38:19.701 --> 38:21.800
Lord Ding, finger torture

38:22.020 --> 38:24.001
is child's play.

38:24.381 --> 38:26.001
What can you uncover with it?

38:30.540 --> 38:34.019
Your reputation for interrogation
precedes you, Lord Song.

38:34.020 --> 38:36.001
No one in the world can rival you.

38:36.301 --> 38:37.721
So tell me,

38:40.060 --> 38:41.681
what method should I use?

39:12.861 --> 39:15.681
Acid, when it touches an open wound,

39:16.821 --> 39:19.121
is excruciatingly painful.

39:40.060 --> 39:42.001
Song Mo is no longer in the military.

39:42.020 --> 39:43.459
Why show him courtesy?

39:43.460 --> 39:45.059
He may no longer hold a position,

39:45.060 --> 39:47.499
but he's still the Duke of Ying's son.

39:47.500 --> 39:49.059
Since the day he was born,

39:49.060 --> 39:50.561
I've had to show him respect.

39:51.060 --> 39:51.920
Yes.

39:52.180 --> 39:53.681
He is enemies with the Dou family,

39:53.861 --> 39:55.800
so letting him settle this matter

39:55.861 --> 39:57.320
might actually be better.

39:57.781 --> 39:58.601
True.

39:59.500 --> 40:00.800
My uncle's death...

40:00.980 --> 40:02.521
Your deception...

40:03.140 --> 40:04.081
Today,

40:05.180 --> 40:06.920
we'll settle the score.

40:07.261 --> 40:09.081
The Miao family and I were able

40:09.861 --> 40:11.161
to run a profitable business

40:11.341 --> 40:13.721
because the Duke of Ding
kept the pirates at bay.

40:13.861 --> 40:15.800
Why would I harm him?

40:18.861 --> 40:20.721
You may think so,

40:21.341 --> 40:23.721
but your uncle, Dou Shishu,

40:23.941 --> 40:26.380
had ambitions beyond his reach.

40:26.381 --> 40:27.561
By killing my uncle,

40:27.821 --> 40:30.019
he could throw the court into chaos

40:30.020 --> 40:32.320
and seize the opportunity
to rise to power.

40:33.500 --> 40:34.521
Power

40:35.381 --> 40:36.659
leads to wealth.

40:36.660 --> 40:37.800
I told you,

40:38.421 --> 40:40.440
don't lump me together
with my fifth uncle.

40:43.140 --> 40:44.300
You befriended me

40:44.301 --> 40:46.161
in order to leak information
to your uncle,

40:46.701 --> 40:48.860
causing the Ding Army to be disarmed.

40:48.861 --> 40:50.840
Shouldn't I doubt you?

41:00.180 --> 41:03.161
Lord Song grew up on the battlefield.

41:03.301 --> 41:05.400
He is truly a savage.

41:06.381 --> 41:08.099
Even toward a helpless girl,

41:08.100 --> 41:09.920
he showed no mercy.

41:14.140 --> 41:15.840
This medicinal powder from the military

41:15.861 --> 41:17.081
will help your hand heal.

41:21.020 --> 41:22.641
At least make some noise.

41:29.540 --> 41:31.800
Be serious, they are listening.

41:32.620 --> 41:33.260
Scold me.

41:33.261 --> 41:34.041
Scold you?

41:34.221 --> 41:35.081
Yes, scold me.

41:38.100 --> 41:39.480
Are you a snake?

41:39.560 --> 41:41.081
You only know how to bite, don't you?

41:41.221 --> 41:43.041
It's my uncle who's scheming.

41:43.060 --> 41:44.721
Why don't you interrogate him?

41:44.941 --> 41:46.440
Why do you only pick on me?

41:48.020 --> 41:50.360
Can't you see he's trying
to cover himself?

41:50.980 --> 41:51.720
I can see that.

41:51.721 --> 41:52.700
But do you have evidence?

41:52.701 --> 41:53.740
Take me to the ship.

41:53.741 --> 41:55.001
I'll find the evidence.

42:10.060 --> 42:11.681
So twisted.

42:11.701 --> 42:13.920
I like it.

42:16.060 --> 42:17.121
There's one more thing.

42:17.741 --> 42:19.880
Sixteen years ago,
before the maritime trade opened,

42:20.180 --> 42:22.601
Futing merchants were struggling
to make a profit.

42:22.861 --> 42:25.001
You were just a young girl in Zhending.

42:25.381 --> 42:27.641
Why did you decide to invest
a huge sum in Futing?

42:28.540 --> 42:29.960
If it wasn't premeditated,

42:30.980 --> 42:33.960
how could you have known my uncle
would eliminate the pirates

42:34.821 --> 42:36.659
and earn massive profits?

42:36.660 --> 42:38.320
It was Mr. Chen's suggestion.

42:38.540 --> 42:39.920
The Duke of Ding was courageous.

42:40.060 --> 42:41.360
He was bound to succeed.

42:43.701 --> 42:45.400
Miao Ansu defended you,

42:45.781 --> 42:47.820
saying that at the start of the year,

42:47.821 --> 42:49.900
you had already said
maritime trade was peaking

42:49.901 --> 42:52.380
and the Futing business
had to be withdrawn quickly.

42:52.381 --> 42:53.400
It seemed

42:54.341 --> 42:56.480
you knew my uncle would die.

42:57.580 --> 42:58.780
I can see it.

42:58.781 --> 43:01.561
You're hiding something from me.

43:01.941 --> 43:04.001
Why won't you tell me?

43:06.500 --> 43:07.360
Speak.

43:25.540 --> 43:28.880
The emperor is cold and unkind,
repaying loyalty with betrayal.

43:29.100 --> 43:31.280
Loyal ministers and brave generals
die in vain.

43:31.821 --> 43:33.440
So why can't the traitor

43:34.500 --> 43:36.400
be me, Song Mo?

43:37.521 --> 43:40.240
♪Can anyone ease♪

43:40.241 --> 43:44.160
♪the pain of goodbye?♪

43:44.161 --> 43:47.781
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

43:48.001 --> 43:51.620
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

43:51.621 --> 43:57.361
♪Will the pain just
weave itself deeper?♪

43:57.471 --> 43:59.260
♪Where can this restless heart
find peace?♪

43:59.261 --> 44:02.400
♪Left alone in an empty hall♪

44:02.401 --> 44:06.221
♪A lifetime chasing fate's lonely call♪

44:06.281 --> 44:10.560
♪Watching seasons fade and storms rise♪

44:10.561 --> 44:13.140
♪It hurts but it's not all for nothing♪

44:13.141 --> 44:14.410
♪My heart is as empty as a quiet street♪

44:14.411 --> 44:17.380
♪Who cares about the path I walk alone?♪

44:17.381 --> 44:21.600
♪Would you take away
the weight of the past?♪

44:21.601 --> 44:23.530
♪Life is fleeting, like morning frost♪

44:23.531 --> 44:26.760
♪Even a moment feels endless with you♪

44:26.761 --> 44:33.081
♪Like a stream flowing steady
through time♪

44:34.861 --> 44:41.771
♪A lone flower falls from the eaves
Moonlight graces steps beneath♪

44:42.231 --> 44:49.521
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

44:49.791 --> 44:53.041
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

44:53.521 --> 44:57.231
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

44:57.251 --> 45:03.111
♪Will the pain just
weave itself deeper?♪

45:03.701 --> 45:04.980
♪In this chaotic world♪

45:04.981 --> 45:07.920
♪Only love lasts♪

45:07.921 --> 45:11.781
♪We'll get through
every challenge together♪

45:11.951 --> 45:16.180
♪No matter how cold
or uncertain the road♪

45:16.181 --> 45:18.760
♪There's nothing to fear
when I'm with you♪

45:18.761 --> 45:19.970
♪My heart feels empty♪

45:19.971 --> 45:22.940
♪But I can hear your voice♪

45:22.941 --> 45:27.160
♪In this life, under moonlight
and across the oceans♪

45:27.161 --> 45:29.631
♪We'll find our way back to each other♪

45:29.661 --> 45:30.510
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:30.511 --> 45:31.410
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:31.411 --> 45:32.400
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)

45:32.401 --> 45:37.951
♪Together, we'll make
every moment count♪
